Package: mouserial
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3-pyqt6, python3-serial, socat
Description: Full-featured Serial Port Debugging Tool
 MOUSART is a full-featured serial port debugging tool built with PyQt6.
 It supports multiple data formats, virtual serial ports, auto-reply,
 data analysis, and more.
 .
 Features:
  - Multiple data display formats (ASCII, HEX, Decimal, Binary)
  - Virtual serial port support (socat-based)
  - Auto-reply functionality
  - Data analysis (Modbus, checksums)
  - Quick command bar
  - Log export
  - Dark/Light theme support
